Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:09.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,NETFLIX オリジナルシリーズ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone has entered the Area?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:17.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黒瀬(くろせ)）\Nエリア内に何者かが入った？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.43,0:00:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they go over Aimoto Dam?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.43,0:00:19.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愛本遮断堰(あいもとしゃだんぜき)を乗り越えてか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:25.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一時的に開放された？\Nどこの情報だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was opened briefly?\NWhere did you get that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:29.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,対策本部のサーバー？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Matter Defense server?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But Nanbara said nobody can get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:33.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何が“何人(なんぴと)たりとも”だ\N南原(なんばら)ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Just talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:36.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや こっちの話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:38.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わざわざ悪かったな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Yes, I know very well. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:43.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってる 分かってますって\Nじゃあ おやすみ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't much I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:46.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とはいえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuya and the rest\Njust left Yanagawara Camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:49.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,雄哉(ゆうや)たちは\N柳河原(やながわら)キャンプを出たばかりで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:52.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,連絡が取れんか…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.13,0:00:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can't contact them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:59.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楓(かえで)）ひゃっほ〜！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You silly Matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.14,0:01:01.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マターちゃんってば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.10,0:01:05.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,コンペなんだから\Nもっと 張り切ってくんないと！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a competition!\NYou have to try harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.19,0:01:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaede! Don't assume Evidence is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.27,0:01:09.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香(はるか)）\N楓！\Nエビデンスをうのみにしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:11.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほいほ〜い！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.78,0:01:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure is having fun.\NShe's forgotten she's the diversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:19.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹(かずき)）\N楽しそうでいいですね\N陽動係だってのも忘れて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting sick of facing\Nthe same damn stuff all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:24.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そろそろ似たようなのばっか\N飽きてきたんですけど〜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Misawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:25.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（篠山(しのやま)）三沢(みさわ)！\N（楓）あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:26.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香）楓！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:40.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤバッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:42.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模(さがみ)）チッ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:51.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:14.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:34.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）\N調子に乗るのも\Nいいかげんにしろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of you\Ngetting carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:37.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）マターの注意をそらす役が―\N（アイコ）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your job is to distract the Matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,not to put the Beetle in danger.\NDamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に ビートルを\N危険にさらしてどうする！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:43.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クライアントと\N仲良くお散歩だけじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just going on strolls with the client
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,won't score you any points either, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっちも点数 稼げないでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:47.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香）ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:52.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楓に有効な情報を提供できなかった\N私のせいでもあるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault for not supplying Kaede\Nwith effective information.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd never seen that kind of\NMatter variation before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:55.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楓）\Nあんなマターの変形\N今までなかったじゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't have known...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:56.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,予測なんて…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:59.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香）\N楓がスタンドプレーに走るのは\N予測できた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew Kaede would show off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:01.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パートナーとして
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,As her partner,\NI should have controlled her better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:03.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと的確に\Nコントロールすべきだった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means\Nyou're still an inexperienced team.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:07.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）\N要するに\Nチームとして未熟ってわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:11.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,く…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白石(しらいし)）まずいわね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:16.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絡みついたマターが\Nアクチュエータの奥まで入り込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Matter has entered the actuator\Nand crystallized.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結晶化してるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to take a while to get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:20.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取り除くのに\N少し時間がかかりそう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:22.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）大丈夫ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,At sunrise tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:25.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明日の日の出の時間になったら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the Matter around K2 will become active.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:27.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,Ｋ２の門番が\N活性化しはじめますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from the timing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:32.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（篠山）\N月齢からして\N門番の最大活性は１週間は続く
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,activity around the gate\Nwill last a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If we get stopped for that long,\Nwe'll run out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:36.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけ足止めを食らえば\Nミッションはタイムオーバーだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:37.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白石）急ぐわ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'll hurry.\N-All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:40.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は川上のマターを見張る
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll watch the Matter on the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:43.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）何だよ あいつ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask, Minase.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:45.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（篠山）水瀬(みなせ)！ ひとつ頼めるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:47.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）はい？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:53.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）\N三沢さんと芹(せり)さんの所 行ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to Misawa and Seri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:55.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）何のために？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:57.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）ひと言 声かけてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:05:00.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私たちのために\N頑張ってもらってるんだもん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:05:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're working hard to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）ここにいろ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで身を危険にさらして
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you put yourself in danger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:06.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼女たちの仕事を増やせば\N本末転倒だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and cause more trouble, there's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガション！）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:20.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）あっ 一樹さん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiko, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:23.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アイコちゃん 平気だった？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:28.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私より…\N三沢さんたち 大丈夫かな？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more worried about Misawa and Seri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:30.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）自業自得だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll get what they deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:31.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sample of the crystallized Matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:36.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マターの結晶化サンプルだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard from Shinoyama
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:38.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,篠山さんから聞いた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're chemically synthesizing\Nvial cartridges on the fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:39.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バイアルカートリッジを
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:42.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,即席で\Nケミカルシンセサイズするって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マジで言ってんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:45.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）ケミカルシンセ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Chemical synthesis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:48.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）\Nカートリッジの調合のことだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how cartridges are prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:51.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）\N新手の情報を\Nタウンに持ち帰れない以上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't deliver\Nthis new data to Town,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:54.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シンセは ここでやるしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to synthesize it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:56.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 何者(なにもん)なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you supposed\Nto not get involved with clients?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:59.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）\Nクライアントには\N深入りしないんじゃなかったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:01.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,く…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:04.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:08.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy really annoys me!\NWho the hell does he think he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:13.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつ ホント マジムカつく！\N偉そうに 何様？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He even involved you, Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:15.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遙香まで巻き添えにしてさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:19.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は自分自身の非を謝罪しただけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I only apologized for my own mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:21.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遙香は何も悪くないじゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:25.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このミッションが終わって\Nタウンに戻れたらさ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When this is over\Nand we return to Town,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you should partner with better people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちゃんとしたヤツと組み直しなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:30.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうしてほしいの？ 楓は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you want, Kaede?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,く…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）\Nこのままだと彼女は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If this keeps up,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:38.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつか必ず 自分に足をすくわれる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll trip herself up someday for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:42.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（篠山）\Nそれも含めて コンペの評価対象だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all part of our evaluation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:43.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）くっそ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:46.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつ 神崎(かんざき)って
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If that Kanzaki wasn't our client,\NI would never work with that jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:49.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クライアントじゃなかったら\Nぜってえ 会いたくないっすよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dream contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:52.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドリームコンタクト？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:56.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,プライマリー･ポイントにいる\Nもう１人の君と
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when your brain links with\Nyour other brain located at Primary Point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:58.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君の脳とを互いにリンクさせる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:03.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１人の君からの情報は\N夢の形で君に入り込み
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Information from the other you\Nis transmitted like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:05.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その夢を観察することで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,By observing those dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:08.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,プライマリー･ポイントの状況を\Nのぞき込むことができる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see what's happening\Nat Primary Point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１人の私と？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The other me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:13.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）心配はいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:17.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すでに君は眠っている間に\N数回 経験している
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You have already experienced this\Nseveral times while sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:22.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前に 閉じ込められている\Nお母さんや弟君の今の様子を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen\Nhow your mother and brother are doing now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,in your dreams, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:24.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夢で見たことがあるだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:27.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それも\Nこのドリームコンタクトの効果だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's part of this Dream Contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:28.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:32.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの夢\Nもう１人の私が見た風景なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Those dreams are what\Nthe other me is seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:34.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）ただし…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,until now, these contacts\Nhave been coincidental and passive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:36.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今までのコンタクトは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:39.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偶然性に頼った\Nパッシブなものだった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:41.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回 行うのは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このビートルの\N演算処理能力を借りた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we will be using\Nthe Beetle's processing unit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:45.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,より精度が高く
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to make a more precise and active contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:48.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,能動性の強い\Nアクティブなコンタクトだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:49.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:54.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）私の脳をコピーして
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My brain was copied,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:08:00.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私と同(おんな)じ思い出を持って\N生み出されたもう１人の橘(たちばな)アイコ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:08:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and there is another Aiko Tachibana\Nwith the same memories as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな気持ちなんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how she feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？ っていうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been observing my dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:09.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神崎君 私の夢のぞいてたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:11.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何それ！ ありえない！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,By what right?\NHow could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:12.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:14.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だって 私の夢でしょ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are my dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew you were going to\Nobserve my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:18.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう のぞくならのぞくって\N先に言ってくれれば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:20.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恥ずかしい夢 見ないように\N頑張ったのに！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've tried\Nnot to have embarrassing ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:23.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 夢と言っても…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling them dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:26.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１人の君の意識が\N流れ込んできているだけだから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but they are only thoughts\Nfrom the other you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:28.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）ふーん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:30.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（南原）分かってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There are other people\Nthat must be placated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:34.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手を打たなきゃならない相手は\Nほかにもいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Matter eradication wing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:35.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊佐津(いさづ)）マター殲滅(せんめつ)派？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And abroad. This affects the economy,\Ninternal affairs, and national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:37.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（南原）海の外にもよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:40.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,経済 内政干渉 国防…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:41.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いざとなったら 政府は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The government will use
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,destruction of the Area\Nto bargain, if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:44.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,エリアの破棄をバーターに\Nしのごうとする
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To protect Japan's\Nartificial organism industry,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:49.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この国の人工生体産業を守るには\N強いカードが必要よ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,we need an ace up our sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:50.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,例えば…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For example,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:54.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,新たな進化を遂げた人工生体が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,showing the world that we've\Nalready achieved
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:57.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すでに完成している事実を\N世に明かす
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a new advancement in artificial organisms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:01.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々の勇み足を棚に上げてか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd have us expose\Nthe advantage we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:06.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（南原）\N得られた魚の大きさを知れば\N世間は口を慎まざるをえない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If people know the size of the fish,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't expect them to keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:11.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのためにも 唯一にして\N最大の成果である橘アイコは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to accomplish this,\NAiko Tachibana, our greatest achievement,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:14.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対に失うわけにはいかないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,must not be lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:18.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まったく\N君の大胆さには感心する
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.\NYou've got a hell of a lot of guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:19.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（南原）ホントね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:24.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし由良俊英(ゆらとしひで)がいれば\Nここまでしなくても済んだのかも
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If Toshihide Yura were still around,\Nthis may not have been necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He is already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:26.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツは もういない！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:33.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,由良は もういないんだ\N由良ノートなんてものも…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yura is gone. And there is\Nno such thing as the Yura Notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That is exactly why\NI will bring back Aiko Tachibana,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:38.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこそ\N私は 必ず橘アイコを取り戻す
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:41.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな手を使ってでもね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:47.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなところで\N終わるわけにはいかない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let this end now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,SCHOOL ORIENTATION CEREMONY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,MUSIC COMPETITION
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} What is this?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）\Nん？ 何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What in the world is all this?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ？ これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:29.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:35.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）神崎君…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:45.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お母さんと亮太(りょうた)に また会えた\N由良先生にも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw Mom and Ryota again.\NAnd Dr. Yura, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:50.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神崎君なら きっと知ってるよね？\N由良先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You must know Dr. Yura, right, Kanzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Toshihide Yura...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:54.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,由良… 俊英
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:58.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）\Nやっぱり…\Nお父さんが言ってたから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad even said,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:11:02.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,若いけど\Nとっても優秀で有名な研究者だって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"He's young,\Nbut he's a very famous researcher."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:07.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 私が会った由良先生は\Nそんな感じじゃなかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Dr. Yura\Nthat I knew wasn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:10.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だか つかみどころのない\N不思議な人だった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He was rather elusive and mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:14.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも おかしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:19.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 由良先生と\Nあんな青空の下で会ったことない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I never saw Dr. Yura outdoors\Nunder a blue sky like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:23.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お父さんの会社が\N桐生(きりゅう)病院でやってた定期検査と
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I only met him at the checkups\NDad's company did at Kiryu Hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:26.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,交通事故の手術のときだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and at the surgery after the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:28.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１人の私だって…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:30.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夢だから？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,from the other me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:34.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か 別の人の思い出みたいだった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed like the memories\Nof a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）疲れただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The mingling of consciousness\Nduring Dream Contact
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:41.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドリームコンタクトによる\N主観意識の交錯は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:42.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脳に負担をかける
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is hard on the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:45.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しばらく休んでいたほうがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You should rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:48.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）\Nううん 休んでなんかいられないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:52.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だって\Nみんなが頑張ってるんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}everyone is working so hard.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to work even harder.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:54.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私はもっと頑張らないと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:59.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私にもできることを何か…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be something I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:01.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（グミ）キュキュイ\N（アイコ）あっ！ あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Gummi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:03.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）グミ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:10.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おなか減ってたんだ　ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You must've been hungry. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:16.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいしい？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, even your brain is\Nan artificial organism, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:22.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ あんたって\Nその脳みそも人工生体なんだよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking? What is it like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:27.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ホント 何考えてんの？\Nどんな気分？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know,\Nthose rations don't have any taste at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:32.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも レーションって\Nちょっぴり味気ないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:33.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:35.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガタン）\Nうん？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:38.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白石）お待たせ　すぐに出るわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:40.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 白石さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiraishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:45.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（篠山）\Nエリア３にダイブインするためには
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To get inside Area Three,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we absolutely must arrive at K2\Nbefore sunrise tomorrow.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:48.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何としても\N明日の日の出時刻までに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:50.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,Ｋ２に到達せねばならない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone must keep that in mind!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:53.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,各位 くれぐれも心してほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If I rehydrate this package,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:57.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）\Nこっちのパックは 水で戻せば
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it will be like mashed potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:59.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マッシュドポテトっぽく\Nなりそうだから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:02.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,温めたチキンの\Nレーションの上にのっけて…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I can add some heated chicken
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:06.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいしい食事で\Nみんなを応援したいか…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's trying to raise morale\Nby making the meals delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:09.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必要なのは 栄養素とエネルギーだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All they need is nutrition and calories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:11.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,余計なことはいいから 席につけ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about it. Sit back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）けど…\N（グミ）キュキュキュ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:16.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）こら！ ダメだって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:20.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:23.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だろう？ 何か… 来る！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is odd.\NIt feels like something's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:25.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:26.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（２人）あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Malignant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:27.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香）マリグナント！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:34.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）エビデンス！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Golf 24 Iota!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:36.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）\Nゴルフ･ツー･フォー･イオタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:39.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香）\N変種パターンが\Nこれまでどおりならね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The mutations still keep coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Area Two positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:40.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（篠山）エリア２ポジション！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Misawa and Seri, divert the Matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:42.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マター陽動は三沢･芹！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:45.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ビートル警護は相模･水瀬！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sagami and Minase, guard the Beetle!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:47.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）あっ 何あれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:48.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白石）マターの天井よ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A Matter ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:51.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫\Nあのマターは ずっと休眠状態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.\NThat Matter has always been dormant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:52.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）待った！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's active!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:54.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,活性化してる！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一同）えっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're flanked above and below.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:00.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）\N上下から挟みうちってわけか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:02.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（篠山）\N猶予はない このまま突っ切る！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop! Charge through!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to knock out whatever we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:05.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楓）\N片っ端から\Nつぶしゃいいってことでしょ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, this isn't your one-man show.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:08.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）\Nいいな？\Nお前一人のショーじゃないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:10.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,余計なお世話！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘヘッ… あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:30.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結晶化… しない？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not crystallizing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This mutation is different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香）\N変種パターンが これまでと違う？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a new type?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:34.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）新種か！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'll hit it from the ceiling!\N-Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:41.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楓）天井のほうから片づける！\N（遙香）分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香）活性度に気をつけて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out for other activity!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）このままだと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If this keeps up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:09.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ビートルに攻撃が及ぶのも\N時間の問題だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll attack the Beetle before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分がヘビーレーザーを！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll man the heavy laser.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:12.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,了解！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:14.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白石）\Nファイア･アシストをリンクする
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll link the fire assist computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:19.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意識の中でターゲットを選択して\Nトリガーを引く
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus on an object to target it,\Nthen pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:20.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけるわね？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And this adjusts power and wavelength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:23.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）出力と波長はこれか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ… また！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:27.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白石）アイコちゃん？\N（アイコ）来る！ そっちから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Aiko?\N-It's coming! From over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:34.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うう… くっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:36.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっち！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-How can you tell?\N-I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:42.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）なぜ分かる？\N（アイコ）分かんない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How come? How can I tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:45.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして… なんで分かるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The laser's vial cartridge\Nand Evidence aren't right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:49.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,レーザーもバイアルカートリッジも\Nエビデンスが合ってねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,None of our weapons are effective!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:51.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香）\N手持ち全種 有効弾がない！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If nothing is effective,\Nwe may as well give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:54.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楓）\N適合すんのなきゃ\Nお手上げじゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:15:59.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ！ サンプルを！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:15:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! I'll get a sample!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:02.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,撃たれたマターの破片があれば
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a piece of Matter we've shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:03.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あった！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:15.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ピピピ…）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:17.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きた！ わっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:19.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:24.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うぐっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:35.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ケミカルシンセ やってみせろよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Chemically synthesize this, Yuya Kanzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:36.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神崎雄哉！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:40.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,受け取った！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:44.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が代わりにレーザー砲を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take over the laser cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:46.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白石）えっ？\N（雄哉）じっとしてろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-Sit still!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That is your most important job!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:49.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが 君がすべき\Nいちばんの仕事だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just sit still!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:56.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何もしないなんて できない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:16:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiraishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:16:59.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,白石さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Patch me into everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:01.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆さんと通信をつなげてください
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:03.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:06.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）あっ…\N相模さん 上です！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sagami, above you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:11.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助かった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:13.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遙香さん 後ろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:15.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:17.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）篠山さん そっち！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinoyama, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:19.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楓さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:24.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楓）\Nいいよ あんた面白いじゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it! This is getting interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kick your butt now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:27.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まとめて お相手してあげる！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:29.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香）\N１人で背負わないで 楓！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't attack it alone, Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's my fault\Nthat we have to make up time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:34.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楓）\Nだって 私のせいで時間が…\N取り戻さなくちゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:35.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's active!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:37.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,活性化！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:39.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:43.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:50.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前一人のショーじゃないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't your one-man show.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help it.\NThis is how I've always done things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:54.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しょうがないじゃん\Nずっと こうやってきたんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent! Now, just hold still!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:09.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）\Nよし！\N頼むから じっとしててくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:10.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香）楓！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:15.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楓）\Nなんで？ ほっとけばいいじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why didn't you leave me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't disgrace my name
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:17.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）名折れになるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:19.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺がいる前で仲間に死なれちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,by letting one of my comrades die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:20.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:22.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）完成した！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:27.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カートリッジは\N無人のバイポッドに運ばせた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cartridges loaded\Nonto an automated bipod!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）了解！ 行くぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:30.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楓）よっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:35.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楓）生き残ってやるわよ！\Nそれで満足？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay alive! Will that satisfy you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:38.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その調子だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:40.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふん！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Your arm!\N-It's artificial anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:43.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香）ちょっ その腕…\N（一樹）義手ですから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's crystallizing!\N-Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:50.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楓）結晶化する！\N（相模）ドンピシャだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:18:58.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ… すごい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:18:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all coming at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 同時に！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:13.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:17.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アイコ）あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes!\N-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:27.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（２人）よし！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:31.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やったわ！\Nん？ アイコちゃん？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Aiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:34.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）橘！\N（白石）アイコちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Tachibana!\N-Aiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:38.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白石）大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:39.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,終わったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:41.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よかった…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:44.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（グミ）キュウ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:46.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（グミ）キュウ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:01.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黒瀬）ああ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:03.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊佐津）\N君には除籍処分が下された
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:08.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理事会の全会一致だ\N当事者である君を除いてね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a unanimous vote by the board\Nof directors, except for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:12.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クビ？ 俺が？ なんで？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been fired? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:15.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心当たりはあるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, you must know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:18.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありすぎて逆に分からんよ\Nどれだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can think of many reasons.\NWhich one was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:24.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,桐生先生の研究予算から\Nお前に流れた金の行き先について
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,With your use of funds\Nfrom Dr. Kiryu's research budget,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:26.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,虚偽の記載が発覚した
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,we discovered falsified records.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.05,0:20:28.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,桐生のおやじさんは？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Dr. Kiryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:33.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊佐津）\N君の裁量に委ねてある旨\Nかばってはおられたが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He defended you by saying its use was\Nat your discretion.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:37.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々としては\N業務規定違反にあたる会計報告を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But we couldn't possibly ignore\Nthe infraction of company rules{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:39.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,放置しておくことはできないのでね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in the accounting report.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:43.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残念だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:46.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黒瀬）しくった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,With me out of the way,\Nnobody will block
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:49.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺をハブりゃ\Nヤツが桐生研のトップに立つのを
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,whoever is running Kiryu Research.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:51.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,邪魔するヤツはいない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem now is the old man's password.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:54.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題は\Nおやじさんの持ってるキーコードだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:58.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,サーバーには\Nあのファイルが残ったままなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those files are still on the server.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれが渡ったら…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that stuff gets out...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:09.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹）\Nまさか お前のケミカルシンセが\N使い物になるとはな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect your chemical synthesis\Nwould come in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was thanks to the data you collected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:12.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄哉）\N君は採取したデータに従ったまでだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:17.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腕まで直しやがって\Nったく 何者だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You even made me a new arm.\NWho the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-How's it going?\N-All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:19.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香）どう？\N（雄哉）終わった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.02,0:21:23.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（遙香）\Nどうして\Nマターの位置が分かったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know\Nwhere the Matter was coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:26.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで… かな？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about that? We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:28.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楓）\Nいいじゃん そんなの\N勝てたんだし！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And you made our rations taste great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:32.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それにレーション\Nここまで化けさせるなんてさ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:33.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すごいよ アイコ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Aiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! This looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:36.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ホント うまそう！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:40.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マターの察知に 意識の喪失…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She senses Matter,\Nbut loses consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:43.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アクティブドリームコンタクトの\N影響だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be the active Dream Contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:44.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありえるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:46.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,可能性は十二分に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's highly probable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:49.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それと もう１つ 気になることが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Something else bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:52.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,プライマリー･ポイントにいる―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears the other Aiko
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,at Primary Point is losing consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:56.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１人の橘アイコの意識レベルが\N低下しているようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:21:57.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.52,0:22:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's likely due\Nto all the recent activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.52,0:21:59.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おそらく 大活性の影響
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:02.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,急がないと たどりつく前に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't hurry,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,she may lose consciousness\Nbefore we arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:05.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼女が意識を\N喪失してしまうかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:07.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなったら 交換手術は…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If she does,\Nthe surgery won't be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:10.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:13.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一樹･遙香）ん？\N（楓）どうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:17.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.75,0:22:20.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（相模）マリグナント！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Malignant!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.79,0:22:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, prepare for action!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:22.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（篠山）各位 対処準備！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! There's something\Non the close-range sensor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.80,0:22:28.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白石）\N待って 近接センサーに別の反応！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.59,0:22:29.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一同）あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.55,0:22:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Heat source at five o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:31.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５時！ 種別 動力熱源！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.10,0:22:32.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（２人）あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.35,0:22:47.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.77,0:24:10.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〜
